{"tid":1837154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎係中國打擊香港抗爭運動既殺著","createTime":"2020-01-23T13:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T17:16:11.000Z","uid":61886,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8be2a4b602dbd5c671d5aa5215cb6ca68c007660","tid":1837154,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"現階段估計<br />\n中國已大規模爆發<br />\n<br />\n香港垃圾政府無諗住處理既態度<br />\n明顯係有政治任務<br />\n<br />\n估計香港最終會大型爆發兼有人死<br />\n<br />\n對抗爭影響<br />\n<br />\n1. 大眾討論焦點轉移 (eg 連登無人推行動post)<br />\n<br />\n2. 抗爭活動出席人數減少 (eg 今日高鐵活動)<br />\n- 肺炎令大眾減少外出<br />\n- 少左人聚焦抗爭<br />\n<br />\n3. 打擊黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 肺炎令大眾上街消費減少<br />\n- 食肆影響最大<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n喺中國入面點爆<br />\n死幾多人 都未必影響到政權<br />\n<br />\n如果大家諗住食住花生爆肺炎<br />\n然後中共玩完<br />\n<br />\nSorry 你太睇少中共<br />\n<br />\n藍絲而家覺得政府幾廢都好<br />\n肺炎一完 都會變返撐政府<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我地除左要保護好自己<br />\n都唔可以放懶左抗爭既心<br />\n<br />\n我地一放鬆落黎<br />\n大清算就好快會到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS2OHKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS2OHKc.jpg&h=09dbecdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"612c857f34881ce182404bb203e59572343919c2","tid":1837154,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自救運動</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66832f5028ea9311e3faeef4cc1598c3d77d1a0","tid":1837154,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"自保啦"},{"pid":"60ce594df6244378db93d774067c24ee6e464da3","tid":1837154,"uid":47080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"係唔係傻㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府唔理咪即係叫更加多人出嚟反政府囉<br />\n革命點嚟